node.title: Police appeal for information on missing Auckland man
node.description: Police have appealed for any information on the whereabouts of 65-year-old Auckland man Atonio Finau, who has been missing for almost a month.
node.content:
["Police have appealed for any information on the whereabouts of 65-year-old Auckland man Atonio Finau, who has been missing for almost a month.", "", "
Missing Auckland man Atonio Finau - CCTV footage [right] shows the clothing he was last known to be wearing. Photo: Supplied
", "Police say Finau was last seen on 16 November, and his family had serious concerns for his welfare.", "A Police spokesperson said his whereabouts remained unknown, "despite a number of enquiries being carried out".", ""Finau lives in the Otahuhu area but drove to Laingholm on Monday 15 November 2021 where he left his car, a black coloured Nissan Murano SUV/wagon.", ""Enquiries have established that on the afternoon of Tuesday 16 November 2021, he caught a bus from Laingholm to the New Lynn bus depot."", "Police said Finau's disappearance was out of character and have appealed for anyone with any sightings of Finau to contact police."]
